00:49:12,390 --> 00:49:14,098
I'm sorry

561
00:49:14,260 --> 00:49:16,596
Aren't you with Takako?

562
00:49:16,620 --> 00:49:18,145
Why are you alone?

563
00:49:19,810 --> 00:49:21,152
What are you doing?

564
00:49:39,215 --> 00:49:39,973
Hello

565
00:49:41,700 --> 00:49:43,840
Thank you for your work.

566
00:49:45,015 --> 00:49:48,015
I received a call from you earlier

567
00:49:48,473 --> 00:49:49,403
What's wrong?

568
00:49:49,931 --> 00:49:51,107
How is your business?

569
00:49:51,132 --> 00:49:54,132
The world is currently in a recession

570
00:49:54,593 --> 00:49:58,105
Well, actually, I just got a call

571
00:49:58,230 --> 00:50:00,366
If you see someone like this staying at your hotel, please contact us immediately.

572
00:50:00,724 --> 00:50:02,191
What did this person do?

573
00:50:02,918 --> 00:50:04,223
It's a car robbery

574
00:50:05,364 --> 00:50:08,543
I have a hard time remembering young people's faces

575
00:50:08,973 --> 00:50:09,958
Yeah

576
00:50:10,614 --> 00:50:11,622
It can't be helped.

577
00:50:18,030 --> 00:50:20,301
Um, I might have seen this somewhere before

578
00:51:17,293 --> 00:51:18,090
Dad

579
00:51:22,321 --> 00:51:25,199
You go somewhere far away,please.

580
00:51:26,960 --> 00:51:29,376
I don't want to trouble you all,

581
00:51:30,205 --> 00:51:37,832
I want to go somewhere far away, but I can't eat there, so I ended up coming back to this town.

582
00:51:40,030 --> 00:51:41,574
Things were better back in the day

583
00:51:43,544 --> 00:51:48,645
If my arm works,
I can run my clothing store like before.

584
00:51:49,122 --> 00:51:50,497
That's my mother's fault.

585
00:51:52,583 --> 00:51:54,028
Don't say like that.

586
00:51:55,363 --> 00:51:56,253
It can't be helped.

587
00:51:57,965 --> 00:52:03,753
She was conscripted and hasn't returned for eight years.

588
00:52:06,979 --> 00:52:08,332
Don't worry

589
00:52:09,942 --> 00:52:11,536
I'll go somewhere eventually

590
00:52:17,690 --> 00:52:20,296
If it's about you all being happy,

591
00:52:20,335 --> 00:52:21,816
I'll do anything

592
00:52:23,387 --> 00:52:25,184
I can't be happy, you know

593
00:52:26,192 --> 00:52:27,145
Why not?

594
00:52:32,960 --> 00:52:35,406
I feel sorry for Dad too, but...

595
00:52:35,430 --> 00:52:38,430
We don't know what will happen from now on

596
00:52:39,153 --> 00:52:42,606
No matter how much we struggle, it seems like nothing can be done

597
00:52:44,114 --> 00:52:46,559
That's my mother's fault.

598
00:52:48,142 --> 00:52:51,142
we're just getting more and more unhappy.

599
00:52:52,708 --> 00:52:56,387
No matter how much we struggle, we have no strength left

600
00:53:00,150 --> 00:53:01,855
Dad went off

601
00:53:02,680 --> 00:53:07,355
After that, our house burned down, and we just kept sinking deeper and deeper,

602
00:53:10,184 --> 00:53:12,609
even though we hadn't done anything wrong

603
00:53:12,634 --> 00:53:13,934
Why is it like this?

604
00:53:35,028 --> 00:53:35,989
What's wrong?

605
00:53:36,905 --> 00:53:37,957
What?

606
00:53:39,442 --> 00:53:40,703
What do you want?

607
00:53:41,563 --> 00:53:42,934
Just stay with me
for a little while

608
00:53:43,579 --> 00:53:44,895
I'll go anywhere you want

609
00:54:01,520 --> 00:54:03,434
What kind of place is this?

610
00:54:04,221 --> 00:54:07,221
Hey,you really gave me a good time last night

611
00:54:09,030 --> 00:54:11,363
Be careful.
You were dazed.

612
00:54:16,550 --> 00:54:17,488
You are stupid.

613
00:54:17,785 --> 00:54:19,098
You little brat!

614
00:54:22,254 --> 00:54:23,504
Give it back to me

615
00:54:31,473 --> 00:54:32,888
Hey!

616
00:54:33,692 --> 00:54:35,192
This is the payment from the other day

617
00:54:38,473 --> 00:54:39,949
Hey! Thief!

618
00:54:46,301 --> 00:54:47,762
That was good.

619
00:54:48,737 --> 00:54:50,863
I feel so relieved now

620
00:54:51,504 --> 00:54:53,441
Let's have fun

621
00:54:53,887 --> 00:54:55,059
What do you mean?

622
00:55:03,121 --> 00:55:04,801
Things aren't going so well

623
00:55:05,426 --> 00:55:07,397
So what will happen now?

624
00:55:08,316 --> 00:55:09,895
This is getting quite interesting, isn't it?

625
00:55:10,610 --> 00:55:11,916
Have a seat

626
00:55:13,142 --> 00:55:17,808
well, if you're calm like that, it's fine. Soon enough, You will be beaten down

627
00:55:17,934 --> 00:55:18,973
She's scary.

628
00:55:19,380 --> 00:55:20,980
I wanted to see your crying face

629
00:55:21,712 --> 00:55:23,051
Come on, take it

630
00:55:24,680 --> 00:55:27,680
What are you guys doing coming to this town?

631
00:55:28,360 --> 00:55:29,801
You guys are very brave.

632
00:55:30,950 --> 00:55:32,646
People become normal, I guess

633
00:55:32,670 --> 00:55:33,785
This is what happens

634
00:55:34,450 --> 00:55:35,175
You are stupid.

635
00:55:40,309 --> 00:55:41,942
Get out

636
00:55:45,042 --> 00:55:46,574
How much?

637
00:55:46,614 --> 00:55:48,371
It's 8 yen

638
00:55:54,280 --> 00:55:55,688
I see

639
00:55:56,640 --> 00:55:58,051
That's how it is.

640
00:55:59,236 --> 00:56:02,856
When a person
becomes mature, it turns out like this

641
00:56:04,066 --> 00:56:09,297
Come on, drink more, there's plenty to go around

642
00:56:11,969 --> 00:56:14,542
You guys are still young

643
00:56:14,942 --> 00:56:17,272
I feel comfortable with you

644
00:56:17,740 --> 00:56:20,625
I've never seen a woman like you
before.

645
00:56:20,960 --> 00:56:22,533
Don't tease me

646
00:56:23,420 --> 00:56:25,983
I respect you

647
00:56:26,989 --> 00:56:28,730
Drink more

648
00:56:30,385 --> 00:56:31,661
Hey come on

649
00:56:31,686 --> 00:56:33,847
I need to eat first

650
00:56:33,872 --> 00:56:35,527
You are guts less

651
00:56:44,017 --> 00:56:44,658
Stop it....

652
00:56:45,053 --> 00:56:46,140
Shut up!

653
00:56:51,786 --> 00:56:54,125
This place has become lively.

654
00:56:56,029 --> 00:56:56,683
Shall we go?

655
00:56:57,791 --> 00:56:59,819
Hey dude

656
00:57:01,268 --> 00:57:02,168
Bill please

657
00:57:23,265 --> 00:57:24,452
Watch out

658
00:57:29,411 --> 00:57:31,060
You bastard!

659
00:57:33,620 --> 00:57:34,680
Just wait a minute

660
00:57:35,730 --> 00:57:37,006
I'm going again

661
00:57:37,030 --> 00:57:38,916
Is there really someone who would sleep with a person like that?

662
00:57:40,898 --> 00:57:46,725
Let's drink some alcohol and be happy.

663
00:57:46,883 --> 00:57:49,256
Bye!
shall we go?

664
00:58:20,733 --> 00:58:24,436
This area is where I grew up.

665
00:58:26,078 --> 00:58:31,571
My daughter is Soliciting clients for prostitution, my father was a vagrant.

666
00:58:35,954 --> 00:58:37,194
Like that

667
00:58:40,539 --> 00:58:41,226
Oh yeah.

668
00:58:45,404 --> 00:58:46,691
Keep drinking

669
00:58:46,840 --> 00:58:47,994
Stop it

670
00:58:48,689 --> 00:58:50,022
What, you are just brat!

671
00:58:51,223 --> 00:58:52,257
You are stupid.

672
00:58:52,730 --> 00:58:53,630
What?

673
00:58:55,360 --> 00:58:57,386
Hey, I need to drink

674
00:58:58,377 --> 00:59:00,617
Yes, let's drink

675
00:59:28,382 --> 00:59:30,087
You've had quite a bit to drink

676
00:59:33,836 --> 00:59:35,730
Where are you all from?

677
00:59:36,661 --> 00:59:37,435
Tokyo

678
00:59:38,602 --> 00:59:39,686
Where are you headed?

679
00:59:40,036 --> 00:59:41,715
We were thinking of going to Shikoku

680
00:59:42,860 --> 00:59:43,872
What for?

681
00:59:45,593 --> 00:59:48,542
A friend of mine runs a ranch

682
00:59:50,243 --> 00:59:52,461
I'm thinking of going there and becoming a cattle rancher

683
00:59:53,811 --> 00:59:54,738
I see.

684
01:00:01,056 --> 01:00:02,846
I see, the countryside is nice, right?

685
01:00:07,197 --> 01:00:08,174
Yeah, the countryside is great

686
01:00:10,163 --> 01:00:13,894
The sun is bright and the sky is really blue

687
01:00:17,853 --> 01:00:22,523
Besides, I hear that the ranch is in a place where you can see the ocean

688
01:00:23,090 --> 01:00:25,153
Yeah, it sounds like a nice place

689
01:00:26,210 --> 01:00:27,461
I've never seen it before

690
01:00:28,640 --> 01:00:30,252
My classmate run

691
01:00:31,400 --> 01:00:32,593
He said I can come anytime

692
01:00:33,046 --> 01:00:33,913
Right?

693
01:00:36,132 --> 01:00:38,938
Hey, can you take me along too?

694
01:00:39,691 --> 01:00:40,953
Really, you?

695
01:00:41,326 --> 01:00:44,670
Yeah, please

696
01:00:48,594 --> 01:00:49,641
Are you serious?

697
01:00:50,321 --> 01:00:51,781
Yes

698
01:00:52,744 --> 01:00:53,705
If you're really interested,

699
01:00:53,743 --> 01:00:54,818
I might consider it

700
01:00:56,909 --> 01:00:57,722
But....

701
01:01:02,934 --> 01:01:05,379
I want to go with my mom and sister, the three of us.

702
01:01:06,652 --> 01:01:07,992
I want to break out of this town

703
01:01:09,440 --> 01:01:10,958
Just the three of you guys, huh?

704
01:01:11,650 --> 01:01:13,626
But who knows...

705
01:01:14,549 --> 01:01:18,678
I can't tell if
you'll have work or not

706
01:01:19,428 --> 01:01:21,672
I think it's better than here, right?

707
01:01:24,673 --> 01:01:27,071
It doesn't matter, does it? Take us with you

708
01:01:27,955 --> 01:01:29,723
Well, I guess ...

709
01:01:30,734 --> 01:01:31,954
Please.

710
01:01:32,270 --> 01:01:34,964
You're quite a bold woman, huh?

711
01:01:38,329 --> 01:01:40,367
So, where does the ship leave from? Huh?

712
01:01:42,540 --> 01:01:44,261
that's, um...

713
01:01:45,100 --> 01:01:48,100
A ferry departs from Kobe, huh?

714
01:01:49,170 --> 01:01:50,841
Stay at my place tonight

715
01:01:51,340 --> 01:01:56,298
I'm going to consult with my mom, so we'll decide quickly, and we can catch the ferry tomorrow, right?

716
01:01:56,918 --> 01:01:57,343
Let's go

717
01:02:27,122 --> 01:02:29,750
with this, open the back of the second floor

718
01:02:30,287 --> 01:02:32,052
and go in, you know which room it is, right?

719
01:02:56,122 --> 01:02:56,896
Welcome back

720
01:02:58,040 --> 01:02:58,780
Welcome back

721
01:02:58,984 --> 01:02:59,684
I'm home.

722
01:03:00,787 --> 01:03:04,235
Business is bad, huh?

723
01:03:04,266 --> 01:03:08,005
I see, eat dinner.
It's ready.

724
01:03:10,166 --> 01:03:14,084
What a feast this is!

725
01:03:14,213 --> 01:03:15,363
That's not it

726
01:03:15,979 --> 01:03:17,525
For Yamada

727
01:03:17,619 --> 01:03:18,199
Oh...

728
01:03:21,202 --> 01:03:22,089
Where's he?

729
01:03:23,352 --> 01:03:25,808
He's playing Mahjong again

730
01:03:38,514 --> 01:03:41,607
There are bed bugs.

731
01:03:42,275 --> 01:03:43,408
I feel itchy

732
01:03:46,415 --> 01:03:49,262
maybe it's better to just tell the truth, right?

733
01:03:50,410 --> 01:03:51,636
Whatever

734
01:03:51,660 --> 01:03:53,145
But I feel sorry for her

735
01:03:53,870 --> 01:03:55,386
Even though they are doing this business properly,

736
01:03:55,410 --> 01:03:57,142
They won't go to Shikoku

737
01:03:58,110 --> 01:03:59,590
She's insane

738
01:04:00,070 --> 01:04:00,823
You think so?

739
01:04:02,318 --> 01:04:03,445
You may be right

740
01:04:05,361 --> 01:04:06,933
But she was serious

741
01:04:09,058 --> 01:04:12,585
well, we can stay here tonight without money.
Isn't that good enough for us?

742
01:04:21,270 --> 01:04:24,270
While we were talking about the Fake Story about ranch earlier,

743
01:04:26,030 --> 01:04:28,596
I really started to hope that it was true

744
01:04:32,590 --> 01:04:35,216
I wish I had a small friend's ranch

745
01:04:35,340 --> 01:04:36,280
Come on.

746
01:04:36,886 --> 01:04:38,917
Hey cheer up

747
01:04:40,400 --> 01:04:42,740
Well, anyway, let's just go to my place, okay?

748
01:04:47,595 --> 01:04:51,309
My place is a poor place with no fields.

749
01:04:55,109 --> 01:04:57,325
But they're probably discussing it down there right now

750
01:05:00,822 --> 01:05:02,598
That's right, Mom

751
01:05:02,890 --> 01:05:03,536
No matter where we go

752
01:05:03,560 --> 01:05:04,916
It's definitely better than now

753
01:05:13,608 --> 01:05:15,922
I haven't said anything until today,

754
01:05:17,100 --> 01:05:19,869
but that Yamada is using us

755
01:05:20,898 --> 01:05:22,064
He's terrible.

756
01:05:23,903 --> 01:05:25,510
So let's go for it

757
01:05:27,492 --> 01:05:29,135
We can work at the ranch

758
01:05:29,860 --> 01:05:31,788
I think there are other jobs available.

759
01:05:33,610 --> 01:05:36,610
Even if I'm poor, I want to live with a bright mindset

760
01:05:38,680 --> 01:05:41,680
Now, Mom, make up your mind

761
01:05:42,258 --> 01:05:43,412
But...

762
01:05:45,145 --> 01:05:47,159
Well, what do you  think about that Yamada guy?

763
01:05:48,177 --> 01:05:49,736
You  think he's a great husband?

764
01:05:51,280 --> 01:05:52,349
He's a terrible man, isn't he?

765
01:05:53,590 --> 01:05:56,590
If it's for money, he would even sell his daughter

766
01:05:58,667 --> 01:06:01,095
Ex dad is wandering around here like that,

767
01:06:02,859 --> 01:06:04,120
and if we stay here like this, we...

768
01:06:04,370 --> 01:06:06,180
I don't know what will happen
from now on

769
01:06:08,103 --> 01:06:10,221
Shi-chan, what do you think?

770
01:06:10,719 --> 01:06:13,818
I'll do anything like my sister says

771
01:06:15,719 --> 01:06:17,430
Once you enter this town,Everything will be over

772
01:06:17,972 --> 01:06:20,193
We get used to the lowly life of the people here,

773
01:06:20,996 --> 01:06:22,719
and no one can escape

774
01:06:23,753 --> 01:06:27,847
We've been like that too.
if I hadn't met those people over there...

775
01:06:28,470 --> 01:06:30,102
I probably wouldn't have been able to make such a decision

776
01:06:30,950 --> 01:06:32,397
Maybe the god of help has come

777
01:06:33,136 --> 01:06:34,443
So let's go!

778
01:06:34,714 --> 01:06:37,040
By the way, what will ex-Dad do
when we go?

779
01:06:37,253 --> 01:06:40,298
It's fine if he comes with us

780
01:06:41,103 --> 01:06:44,115
Anyway, please make up your mind

781
01:06:45,038 --> 01:06:48,243
I guess I need to make up my mind

782
01:07:04,910 --> 01:07:06,473
How's your business?

783
01:07:06,808 --> 01:07:07,864
Thanks.

784
01:07:09,208 --> 01:07:10,028
Good evening.

785
01:07:10,394 --> 01:07:11,096
Good evening.

786
01:07:13,462 --> 01:07:14,362
Shi-chan

787
01:07:16,299 --> 01:07:19,904
You're doing great job

788
01:07:20,011 --> 01:07:20,818
Hey.

789
01:07:28,442 --> 01:07:29,369
Shall we go to the second floor?

790
01:07:30,152 --> 01:07:31,088
Yeah

791
01:07:35,050 --> 01:07:37,091
We are going out on the second floor

792
01:07:37,811 --> 01:07:38,664
Go ahead

793
01:07:48,390 --> 01:07:49,880
This time it should be okay, right?

794
01:07:50,273 --> 01:07:52,764
Leave it to me.
Don't worry.

795
01:07:53,016 --> 01:07:54,503
I can't count on it

796
01:07:57,673 --> 01:07:59,189
I tell you

797
01:07:59,220 --> 01:08:00,493
Yesterday's expenses were wasted.

798
01:08:03,765 --> 01:08:05,491
My 2000yen?

799
01:08:05,516 --> 01:08:07,679
Don't care.
I'll throw in three beers for you.

800
01:08:09,344 --> 01:08:11,216
It can't be helped.

801
01:08:12,801 --> 01:08:14,593
I need to call her.
Hold on.

802
01:08:16,146 --> 01:08:18,666
Mom, We made up our mind

803
01:08:20,334 --> 01:08:21,401
We don't need any luggage.

804
01:08:21,820 --> 01:08:23,104
Just go as you are

805
01:08:30,108 --> 01:08:31,295
Bring us beer

806
01:08:31,546 --> 01:08:32,546
3 of beers

807
01:08:33,992 --> 01:08:34,538
Takako.

808
01:08:35,127 --> 01:08:37,240
You should come and check.

809
01:08:37,833 --> 01:08:38,920
What are you doing?

810
01:08:44,002 --> 01:08:44,815
Shizuko.

811
01:08:45,595 --> 01:08:48,938
The customer says they'd like to have a beer with you.

812
01:08:53,793 --> 01:08:55,010
Hurry up.

813
01:08:56,702 --> 01:09:00,824
Now put on your glasses
and stand up, stand up

814
01:09:09,940 --> 01:09:11,050
I'll help you

815
01:09:11,075 --> 01:09:11,676
Don't worry.

816
01:09:12,480 --> 01:09:13,957
Take this

817
01:09:15,310 --> 01:09:16,486
You guys have something to do, right?

818
01:09:16,510 --> 01:09:18,761
Work hard

819
01:09:19,707 --> 01:09:20,598
Let's go

820
01:09:37,472 --> 01:09:38,835
Don't worry.

821
01:09:39,310 --> 01:09:41,003
She'll be fine

822
01:09:45,176 --> 01:09:46,520
Watch your step

823
01:09:58,871 --> 01:10:02,895
There is one person to bring along.

824
01:10:04,004 --> 01:10:05,996
This inn has a hot spring mark( means red light).

825
01:10:12,215 --> 01:10:15,215
I wonder what they're going to do

826
01:10:16,759 --> 01:10:19,285
It would be nice
if they at least brought some tea

827
01:10:19,651 --> 01:10:22,487
She said we can stay here for free.

828
01:10:22,660 --> 01:10:23,753
We won't interfere or anything

829
01:10:24,370 --> 01:10:25,707
I'm sure it's a secret from her dad

830
01:10:27,037 --> 01:10:28,644
I sobered up

831
01:10:32,690 --> 01:10:33,808
Drink beer

832
01:10:45,605 --> 01:10:48,246
Seeing Shi-chan like this,
She's quite beautiful too

833
01:10:49,304 --> 01:10:52,304
You should thank him.
He'll take care of you

834
01:10:52,676 --> 01:10:53,762
Thank you very much.

835
01:10:54,809 --> 01:10:56,129
Please give him a drink

836
01:10:58,301 --> 01:10:59,238
Here

837
01:11:00,800 --> 01:11:02,650
It's ok

838
01:11:03,707 --> 01:11:04,996
Take your time

839
